# Early Construction

A lot of the early stuff needed to build bases, so pipes, basic inserters, basic belts, ammo, power poles and assemblers.  This is a quarter module so can share space with other modules.

Balance between early construction items such as yellow belts v.s. red-belts can be adjusted using logic circuits.  The default is to bias towards keeping a supply of early construction
items over later ones.
